You update your description as follows: 1970s analog remaster with tape-warm sheen, presence-forward centered lead vocals, preserved transients and generous headroom. Gentle limiting, transparent mastering, wide natural imaging, tactile midrange and elastic, walking bass prioritize lyric immediacy, era-faithful harmonies and clear instrument separation.

